data.description: This stunning home is just two years young. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with a spacious 3 car garage, this home is move in ready! Entertain in style in the open kitchen that is complete with vaulted ceilings, kitchen island, pantry, and stainless steel appliances all that create an inviting atmosphere. Enjoy the ambiance of the living room with ample natural light and gorgeous fireplace.  Venture downstairs to the finished basement for additional living space and step outside to the deck, opening to a flat, fully fenced backyard. Skip the wait for new construction, this home is ready to go now!  AMA
